The CPP pool is an introduction for c++ progeramming language, every module is a set of exercises thats cover one or many concepts on cpp.

The cpp module 01 will cover:
*dynamique memory allocation on cpp
*the refference and pointers 
*pointers to member attributes
*switch statement 

